Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体无法随心所欲…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听使唤…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 去感觉法夫那的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他融为一体！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 今天也听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我修理就没问题罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了 你是说真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回答看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐园 - 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.74,0:03:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经出去罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是社团的晨间练习吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说过今天没有练习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是去羽佐间同学家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你走了之后 我就被妈妈骂了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她担心真矢会因为我而迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一小段路冲刺一下就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把这种事放在心上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 看来你比昨天有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咲良要到学校去上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以翔子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没办法来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她一定很快就会好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就拜托你罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书非常重要喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是今天早上回来的吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我在CDC打报告 所以回来得晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各方面都辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学到了不少东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的夕阳颜色似乎会很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城同学 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我刚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那是最新的一集？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等好久罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城 东京很好玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也没什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有碰到什么艺人之类的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一下课就跟近藤同学出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士已经回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没办法再来我家玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是春日井甲洋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你们先自习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自习？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是还有人没来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 他们在别的避难所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚尔维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系统全部上线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命体振动波确认 立即传送
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标质量增加中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人面狮身型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚未起动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用质量测定搜索敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发布红色警戒 执行第三种战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员进行第三种战斗配置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备展开波动屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除伪装镜面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那边没有避难所的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装镜面解除完毕 开启第一波动屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民全部疏散完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已确定93.7%的居民疏散完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽速准备迎击！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色大地部队 请尽快出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 大家都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再20秒就可以出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点喔 亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定对方为敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝色大地部队 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事情 怎么连小酷都逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小酷一定躲到安全的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也赶快去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标接触第一波动屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输出功率降低 要被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动集群防御系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集群防御系统启动完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标继续前进中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标进入肉眼可辨识的范围
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将传送到荧幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是异界体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是异界体…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 并不是这样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单体密度2.33 原子量28.0855
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴性度1.8 质量固定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界体即将实体化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽并不代表会是人类的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波动屏障的负荷上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有75%的机率会在十秒内与敌人的频率同调
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所预测位置的误差20
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏障一解除便展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成两组攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靶子这么大 没打中的不准吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没打中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动被猜到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标从上空接近第二波动屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会变成怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕什么 有点骨气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间她们不会有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以待在那种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点躲进亚尔维斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔维斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向岛的自律迎击系统被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今只能让那个巨人觉醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备进入法夫那启动阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正搭乘电磁弹舱往停机库移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子也曾经驾驶法夫那喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电磁弹舱信号于龙宫岛南方250公尺附近消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员以及工作人员一名目前生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标正前往法夫那机库
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算先破坏巨人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动刚瑠岛上的EPM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能阻止它的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统准备完毕 发射EPM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸 我来驾驶法夫那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事只有你才做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐格飞系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以吧 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚瑠岛EPM 再两分钟之后到达极限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神之岩的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是没办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快准备迎击用的反战车飞弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多撑一分钟 甚至一秒钟就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是现阶段的最适合人选
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EPM输出功率降低
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是法夫那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中为了保护宝藏 而化身为龙的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承这个巨人之名而研发 以对抗异界体的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要防止异界体的读心能力 唯有以法夫那与其对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你以它来守护这座岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 我办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定知道 你的身体可以跟法夫那合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今要守护这座岛 只能仰赖法夫那了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今能办得到的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的办得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 单机作战准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO.11巨龙之洞准备开启
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入齐格飞系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这个数值看来不穿协同作用服也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-加油吧\N-好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动尼贝龙根吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼贝龙根…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认得…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认得它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输入对数螺旋形成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行协同线路认证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼贝龙根启动确认 连接齐格飞系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第三机库
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器运输用的密码被锁定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用武器必须用生体解除钥匙来解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样法夫那不就手无寸铁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁 之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是直接进入你的大脑视听区
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在法夫那体内的你以及在齐格飞里面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此的大脑皮质神经细胞处于直接连结的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有协同作用服 所以连结状态并不完全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今最重要的是让你和法夫那合为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先张开你的眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 法夫那的眼睛就是你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 那家伙快来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启NO.11巨龙之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark XI 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的旅程就这样开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们能够侥幸生还
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿我们不会忘记至今的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到将来这座岛屿恢复为原本乐园的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
